  "content": "<h2>Anki 制卡</h2><ul><li data-pid=\"Y-MrwDCh\">两万五千字长文，你最好的制卡参考书：</li></ul><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/434074509\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-3fc5e91c7a88c26207775c8301afbe1f_qhd.jpg\" data-image-width=\"1579\" data-image-height=\"328\" class=\"internal\">叶峻峣：如何写出好卡片：利用间隔重复创造理解</a><h2>Anki 下载</h2><p data-pid=\"8zp37biM\">百度云：</p><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//pan.baidu.com/s/16JFHGO9Yk1hlUD1d84iCGA\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"visible\">pan.baidu.com/s/16JFHGO</span><span class=\"invisible\">9Yk1hlUD1d84iCGA</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a><p data-pid=\"lTz_rDfu\">iOS 在 AppStore 上售价为 163 元，有能力可以支持一下。</p><h2>B 站 Ankidroid 视频教程（没有声音，请关注操作）</h2><ol><li data-pid=\"09GAluYs\">下载与安装：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.bilibili.com/video/av41518619/%3Fp%3D1\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://www.</span><span class=\"visible\">bilibili.com/video/av41</span><span class=\"invisible\">518619/?p=1</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a></li><li data-pid=\"rLIBPpH2\">创建牌组：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.bilibili.com/video/av41518619/%3Fp%3D2\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://www.</span><span class=\"visible\">bilibili.com/video/av41</span><span class=\"invisible\">518619/?p=2</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a></li><li data-pid=\"LNnbnsSY\">制作问答卡片：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.bilibili.com/video/av41518619/%3Fp%3D3\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://www.</span><span class=\"visible\">bilibili.com/video/av41</span><span class=\"invisible\">518619/?p=3</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a></li><li data-pid=\"6KrYW5hI\">问答卡片学习演示：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.bilibili.com/video/av41518619/%3Fp%3D4\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://www.</span><span class=\"visible\">bilibili.com/video/av41</span><span class=\"invisible\">518619/?p=4</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a></li><li data-pid=\"3stfYL2i\">制作填空卡片与效果演示：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.bilibili.com/video/av41518619/%3Fp%3D5\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://www.</span><span class=\"visible\">bilibili.com/video/av41</span><span class=\"invisible\">518619/?p=5</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a></li><li data-pid=\"aUCIemdn\">在已有卡片的基础上创建父牌组：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.bilibili.com/video/av41518619/%3Fp%3D6\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://www.</span><span class=\"visible\">bilibili.com/video/av41</span><span class=\"invisible\">518619/?p=6</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a></li><li data-pid=\"qY1VljvG\">同时创建父牌组和子牌组：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.bilibili.com/video/av41518619/%3Fp%3D7\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://www.</span><span class=\"visible\">bilibili.com/video/av41</span><span class=\"invisible\">518619/?p=7</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a></li><li data-pid=\"kXJhl3m7\">将从QQ群下载的牌组文件导入到 AnkiDroid：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.bilibili.com/video/av41518619/%3Fp%3D8\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://www.</span><span class=\"visible\">bilibili.com/video/av41</span><span class=\"invisible\">518619/?p=8</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a></li><li data-pid=\"1b6gibYc\">找到百度云下载的牌组文件：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.bilibili.com/video/av41518619/%3Fp%3D9\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://www.</span><span class=\"visible\">bilibili.com/video/av41</span><span class=\"invisible\">518619/?p=9</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a></li><li data-pid=\"5e9-GonS\">为单个牌组设置独立的选项组(学习计划)和设置新卡片数量：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.bilibili.com/video/av41518619/%3Fp%3D10\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://www.</span><span class=\"visible\">bilibili.com/video/av41</span><span class=\"invisible\">518619/?p=10</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a></li><li data-pid=\"pIIV9q-L\">修改共用的选项组(学习计划)将在共用选项组的牌组中生效：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.bilibili.com/video/av41518619/%3Fp%3D11\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://www.</span><span class=\"visible\">bilibili.com/video/av41</span><span class=\"invisible\">518619/?p=11</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a></li><li data-pid=\"r_-90dYK\">将同一个选项组应用到某父牌组的所有子牌组：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.bilibili.com/video/av41518619/%3Fp%3D12\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://www.</span><span class=\"visible\">bilibili.com/video/av41</span><span class=\"invisible\">518619/?p=12</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a></li><li data-pid=\"wYm5aKzv\">设置好选项组(学习计划)后的学习演示：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.bilibili.com/video/av41518619/%3Fp%3D13\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://www.</span><span class=\"visible\">bilibili.com/video/av41</span><span class=\"invisible\">518619/?p=13</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a></li></ol><hr/><h2>电子书(全平台教程)目录（大部分精华都收录了）</h2><ul><li data-pid=\"fRGXmIoU\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.kancloud.cn/ankigaokao/ankigaokao/784948\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">第 0 章 可有可无的话</a></li><ul><li data-pid=\"j458gV0O\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.kancloud.cn/ankigaokao/ankigaokao/784949\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">0.1 Anki X 高考</a></li><li data-pid=\"aglF0OXy\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.kancloud.cn/ankigaokao/ankigaokao/784950\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">0.2 这本书值得读吗？</a></li><li data-pid=\"_vd3Um9z\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.kancloud.cn/ankigaokao/ankigaokao/784951\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">0.3 前言</a></li></ul><li data-pid=\"6Agp3HDX\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.kancloud.cn/ankigaokao/ankigaokao/784952\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">第 1 章 了解 Anki X 高考</a></li><ul><li data-pid=\"eGPsLim4\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.kancloud.cn/ankigaokao/ankigaokao/784658\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">1.1 Anki 是什么？</a></li><li data-pid=\"qsx86Im8\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.kancloud.cn/ankigaokao/ankigaokao/784659\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">1.2 高考是什么？</a></li><li data-pid=\"R9_JRUFM\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.kancloud.cn/ankigaokao/ankigaokao/784660\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">1.3 为什么用 Anki 备战高考？</a></li></ul><li data-pid=\"hdxiQCvc\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.kancloud.cn/ankigaokao/ankigaokao/784661\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">第 2 章 准备工作</a></li><ul><li data-pid